@startuml seq_29_manage_platform
title Sequence Diagram: UC-29 Manage Platform (Admin Login/Logout)

actor Admin
participant "Admin Web" as Frontend
participant "Admin Auth Controller" as Controller
participant "Admin Auth Service" as Service
participant "Admin Repo" as Repo
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis

Admin -> Frontend: (1.1/2.1) Enter Admin Credentials
Frontend -> Controller: (2.2) POST /api/admin/auth/login
Controller -> Service: (3.1) Admin Login
Service -> Repo: (3.2) Fetch Admin by username
Repo --> Service: (3.3) Admin found (hashed_password)
Service -> Service: (3.4) Verify password & Admin Role
Service -> Service: (4.1) Generate Admin Access & Refresh Tokens
Service -> Redis: (4.2) Store Admin Auth State (Refresh Token)
Service --> Controller: (5.1) Tokens
Controller --> Frontend: (5.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: (5.3) Redirect to Admin Dashboard

... Admin manages platform ...

Admin -> Frontend: (6.1) Click Logout
Frontend -> Controller: (6.2) POST /api/admin/auth/logout
Controller -> Service: (7.1) Admin Logout
Service -> Redis: (7.2) Delete Admin Auth State (Revoke Session)
Service --> Controller: (8.1) Success
Controller --> Frontend: (8.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: (8.3) Redirect to Admin Login Page
@enduml
